description:
Join Mackenzie Drebit's presentation, Our High Calling, and discover valuable lessons of faith. This discussion delves into Daniel's principles offering unique insights. Learn answers to essential questions: What is the Three Angels’ Message? When did the judgment start? And what is the significance of the Midnight Cry? 
Mackenzie shares divine guidance and offers principles to shape our lives in today's world. Join us as we explore these crucial topics and uncover lessons that will enhance your faith and spiritual insight!
